{"tid":1497581,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【藍絲食店】鯉魚門茶餐廳網民負評後懷疑買like洗底 老闆娘堅定撐警：我到而家都仲撐警察","createTime":"2019-08-23T04:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T05:12:20.000Z","uid":113761,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b80d0ae243a4501bc4384cd08799f16390f664fb","tid":1497581,"uid":113761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:33:53.000Z","msg":"鯉魚門開業五十多年的銀龍咖啡茶座，過往以獨創腐乳多士及懷舊氣氛聞名，最近就因老闆娘Kate撐警，在撐警集會中主動上台表態支持的立場，惹起不少網民評論。<br />\n<br />\n食評網站上，本地食客及內地網民因Kate立場而展開對罵，Kate在接受其他傳媒採訪時，一方面表明堅定立場，一方面表示最近有不少客人上門支持她，認定自己沒有做錯。<br />\n<br />\n在8月20日，有警員涉及向長者施以酷刑的閉路電視片段被廣傳，引來全城嘩然。在此情況下，到底Kate立場會否有改變﹖記者到訪茶餐廳時，Kate正接受新華社採訪，而她得知記者是蘋果日報旗下員工後，拒絕接受訪問，但在電話訪問中，Kate仍認為警察沒有做錯﹕「我撐好警察。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪﹕《飲食男女》編輯組<br />\n攝影﹕《飲食男女》攝影組<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/etw/magazine/article/20190821/3_59953974/?utm_campaign=etw_social_etw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fetw%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20190821%2F3_59953974%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Detw_social_etw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1XwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=5171c19a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fetw%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20190821%2F3_59953974%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Detw_social_etw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook&h=e54846be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/etw/magazine/article/20190821/3_59953974/?utm_campaign=etw_social_etw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢間野Google reviews</span><br />\n <span style=\"font-size: small;\">懷疑</span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">買正評，今個月全部大陸人名俾評價，由本身2.5分負評推到4.4分！！！ </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n2u3O5G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn2u3O5